flowchart TD
    Start([Mulai]) --> Source{Sumber tugas}

    Source -->|Manual oleh<br/>supervisor| ManualPath["/rooms tab Housekeeping<br/>Klik 'Add Task'"]
    Source -->|Otomatis post-checkout| AutoCheckout[Trigger oleh<br/>checkout flow]
    Source -->|Otomatis daily| DailyCron[Cron / scheduled<br/>run_daily_housekeeping_tasks]

    ManualPath --> ManualForm[Isi: room, task_type<br/>priority, assigned_to,<br/>estimated_duration, notes]
    ManualForm --> ManualValid{Field valid?}
    ManualValid -->|Tidak| ManualErr[Error]
    ManualErr --> ManualForm
    ManualValid -->|Ya| InsertTask[(INSERT housekeeping_tasks<br/>status='pending')]

    AutoCheckout --> AutoTask[(INSERT task<br/>task_type=checkout<br/>priority=high<br/>auto-assign)]

    DailyCron --> DailyTasks[(INSERT batch tasks<br/>untuk semua kamar occupied<br/>task_type=daily)]

    InsertTask --> ListView[Task muncul di list]
    AutoTask --> ListView
    DailyTasks --> ListView

    ListView --> StaffView[HK Staff buka /rooms<br/>tab Housekeeping<br/>filter: assigned_to=me]
    StaffView --> PickTask[Pilih tugas dari list]
    PickTask --> StartTask[Klik 'Start Task']
    StartTask --> UpdProgress[(UPDATE status=in-progress<br/>started_at=NOW)]

    UpdProgress --> PhysicalWork[Kerjakan tugas fisik<br/>di kamar]
    PhysicalWork --> Finished{Tugas<br/>selesai?}
    Finished -->|Belum| Pause[Pause / lanjut nanti]
    Pause --> StaffView
    Finished -->|Ya| MarkDone[Klik 'Complete']

    MarkDone --> UpdComplete[(UPDATE status=completed<br/>completed_at=NOW)]
    UpdComplete --> CheckType{task_type<br/>= 'checkout'?}

    CheckType -->|Ya| FreeRoom[(UPDATE rooms<br/>status=available)]
    CheckType -->|Tidak| NoFree[Status kamar tetap]

    FreeRoom --> RTUpdate[Realtime sync ke<br/>occupancy + dashboard]
    NoFree --> ListView2[Refresh task list]
    RTUpdate --> ListView2
    ListView2 --> Continue{Tugas lain?}
    Continue -->|Ya| StaffView
    Continue -->|Tidak| End([Selesai])

    classDef startEnd fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#10b981
    classDef decision fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#f59e0b
    classDef action fill:#dbeafe,stroke:#3b82f6
    classDef db fill:#e0e7ff,stroke:#6366f1
    classDef auto fill:#fce7f3,stroke:#ec4899
    classDef error fill:#fee2e2,stroke:#ef4444

    class Start,End startEnd
    class Source,ManualValid,Finished,CheckType,Continue decision
    class ManualPath,ManualForm,ListView,ListView2,StaffView,PickTask,StartTask,PhysicalWork,Pause,MarkDone,RTUpdate,NoFree action
    class InsertTask,AutoTask,DailyTasks,UpdProgress,UpdComplete,FreeRoom db
    class AutoCheckout,DailyCron auto
    class ManualErr error
